        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         When I first talked to
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkM2OrCAQhZ-mWRp-RNoFi9nMa5gSim7SCgbKa3z7i-1iEnKoUKk6nM8B4SuX0265ErtkonNDm_CoCxJhYXvFMkVvxSCfSvcj87b34qmfLNYpFMQV4mKp7Mi2fV6iA4o5fSc4l5q9bdCjM-Ck8KAwGC5nqcA47ZzxYQ7m9oXdR0wOLf7DcuaEbLFvoq0-1M9D_rZzHEe3xPRBH1Pn8tqeYmpCLUDBWGurWbSSS8GNHIXUg-Kd6AY_DDxo5KMfAYRBY7TBmWsIwgRwj56vL9nVfa4E7nOtZsWmTHMuMb1a-_OGFZdvo2Wc2r3uKdI5YYJ5QX_Hp5viF8j0woSl0fUT0MXOtM_0fFS9vOM2PmpUF1DJmrPPbSr9mf4HDjuJ8w" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Tory Reiss
         </a>
         back in December, he was in the early stages of starting a new company. Since then, he and the company\xe2\x80\x99s all-star team of co-founders raised a little money, went into the lab, and built. In June, he reached back out to tell me that it was almost ready, and asked if I could help explain what they\xe2\x80\x99re doing. I said yes. We picked a date: July 29th. (That\xe2\x80\x99s today.)
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         We had no way of knowing then that today was going to be Robinhood\xe2\x80\x99s first day of trading as a public company.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Nor did we know that
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkU2OwyAMhU9TdlRA-EkWLGYz14gccBrUhFTgdNQ5_ZB2MRLCCPP8zOcAhLe9vPxjr8TObaTXA33Gn7oiERZ2VCxjil5a1XdGDyx6HWVvepbqOBfEDdLqqRzIHse0pgCU9vxWCKEMW7wyatJ9L7WV1jmrtOvnYDrnJiXnKOLHF46YMAf0-MTy2jOy1S9Ej3rpvi7quy3CsIRy5LBcw761CyWUbEG49_l8kQgyf8J6YORAXBuxcagcpP3lK0Ks3PQbbz9KWPnUFCz5s4pwapDK2E5c5dVGa8VsUAxxAJAOnTMOJ2Fglm6GcNFiu6lrPaZKEO5nM6z4vNO0l5RvLX1fYMP1nWhMxha3Iyd6jZhhWjF-cNGH-hvgeMOMpU0jjkAna9ea0WLotPrgaTy7oTsHoFhzjntT5X_TP3lZlVs" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
