         </a>
         a $58M a16z-led Series B valuing the company at a $450M valuation last week.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         And even with all of the world\xe2\x80\x99s crystal balls at our disposal we could never have guessed that a tweet about capital allocators, of all things, was going to take Twitter by storm.
        </p>
